    imaginary
    Imaginary Part
    
      imaginary
    
    application
    
      This symbol represents unary function used to construct the imaginary part of a
      complex number, i.e. the y component in x+iy.
    

    
      
        ForAll( [x,y], Imaginary(x + i*y) = y )
      
      
        
          
          
